*** Keywords ***
19-4-Setup
    Set Environment Variable  ESX_VERSION  3620759
    ${esx1}  ${esx1-ip}=  Deploy Nimbus ESXi Server  %{NIMBUS_USER}  %{NIMBUS_PASSWORD}
